      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a project car with plenty of potential? This vehicle is ready for a dedicated new owner to give it the mechanical and cosmetic attention it needs to get back on the road! It's a great opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper to make their own.",
