      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a concours-level standard. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Meticulously inspected and preserved, this vehicle offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    }
